#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "&konquest; is the &kde; version of Gnu-Lactic. Players conquer other "
#| "planets by sending ships to them. The goal is to build an interstellar "
#| "empire and ultimately conqueror all other player's planets. &konquest; "
#| "can be played against other people or a computer."
msgid ""
"&konquest; is the &kde; version of &gnu-lactic;. Players conquer other "
"planets by sending ships to them. The goal is to build an interstellar "
"empire and ultimately conqueror all other player's planets. &konquest; can "
"be played against other people or a computer."
msgstr ""
"&konquest; je &kde;-ova verzija Gnu-Latic-a. Igrači osvajaju druge planete "
"šaljući brodove na njih. Cilj je napraviti intergalaktičko carstvo i "
"osvojiti sve planete drugih igrača. &konquest; se može igrati protiv drugih "
"ljudi ili protiv kompjutera."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:108
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Play"
msgstr "Kako igrati"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start &konquest;, press <guibutton>New</guibutton> to start a new "
"game. You will see a dialog in which you need to enter various information "
"to setup your game. Listed below are the following parameters for the new "
"game:"
msgstr ""
"Kada pokrenete &konquest; pritisnite <guibutton>New</guibutton> da počnete "
"novu igru. Pojavit će vam se dialog u koji morate unijeti razne informacije "
"da podesite vašu igru.Ispod su navedeni sljedeći parametri za novu igru:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:116
#, no-c-format
msgid "Players"
msgstr "Igrači"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Amount of players with <guibutton>Add</guibutton> or <guibutton>Remove</"
"guibutton> players"
msgstr ""
"Broj igrača sa <guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton> ili <guibutton>Ukloni</"
"guibutton> igrače"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Names of players"
msgstr "Imena igrača"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type of players (Computer versus Human)"
msgstr "Tip igrača(Kompjuter protiv čovjek)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "Difficulty of computer players (Low/Normal/Hard)"
msgstr "Težina (Lahko/Normalno/Teško)"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the name of the player, double-click in the <guilabel>Name</"
"guilabel> column and edit it. To change the type of the player, open the "
"drop-down list by double-clicking in the <guilabel>Type</guilabel> column. "
"It is also possible to select the type of the new players using the drop-"
"down list of the <guibutton>Add</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Da promijenite ime igrača, dupli klik u  <guilabel>Name</guilabel> kolonu i "
"promijenite ga. Da promijenite tip igrača otvorite padajuću listu duplim "
"klikom u <guilabel>Type</guilabel>  kolonu. Također je moguće odabrati tip "
"novih igrača koristeći padajuću listu <guibutton>Add</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are two types of the human players in &konquest;, namely "
"<guimenuitem>Human (Player)</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Human "
"(Spectator)</guimenuitem>. The latter option allows watching the game "
"without taking part in it."
msgstr ""
"Postoje dva tipa ljudskih igrača u &konquest; , <guimenuitem>Human (Player)</"
"guimenuitem> i <guimenuitem>Human (Spectator)</guimenuitem>. Druga opcija "
"omogućava gledanje igre bez učešća."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The type of AI player can be chosen from <guimenuitem>Default (Weak)</"
"guimenuitem> (a player that is neither aggressive in attacks nor in "
"defense), <guimenuitem>Default (Offensive)</guimenuitem> (an aggressive "
"attacking player) and <guimenuitem>Default (Defensive)</guimenuitem> (a "
"player with defensive strategy)."
msgstr ""
"Tip AI igrača se može odabrati iz <guimenuitem>Default (Weak)</"
"guimenuitem>(igrača koji nije agresivan ni u napadu ni u odbrani), "
"<guimenuitem>Default (Offensive)</guimenuitem>(agresivan napadački igrač) i "
"<guimenuitem>Default (Defensive)</guimenuitem>(igrač sa defanzivnom "
"strategijom)."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Besides these classic AI players, <guimenuitem>Becai (Balanced)</"
"guimenuitem> is a balanced player taking most of <xref linkend=\"strattips\"/"
"> into account."
msgstr ""
"Pored ovih klasičnih AI igrača, <guimenuitem>Becai (Balanced)</guimenuitem> "
"je balansirani igrač koji u obzir uzima <xref linkend=\"strattips\"/>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keep in mind that the actual difficulty of any opponent depends on your very "
"own strategy. If you play aggressively yourself, an aggressive AI player "
"might be easier to defeat than a defensive player, and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"Imajte na umu da stvarna težina protivnika zavisi i od vaše strategije. Ako "
"igrate agresivno, agresivnog AI igrača će te možda lakše pobijediti nego "
"defanzivnog igrača i suprotno."

