#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Pravila Igre, Strategija i Savjeti"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rules"
msgstr "Pravila"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ships cannot be stopped once they leave a planet."
msgstr "Brodovi ne mogu biti zaustavljeni jednom kada napuste planet."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ships cannot attack other ships in midair."
msgstr "Brodovi ne mogu napasti druge brodove u zraku."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ships can be stored at planets for later use."
msgstr "Brodovi ne mogu biti pohranjeni na planetama za kasniju upotrebu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "A planet cannot be given away."
msgstr "Planete ne može biti poklonjena."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A player can skip a turn by pressing <guibutton>End Turn</guibutton> without "
"launching any ships."
msgstr ""
"Igrač može preskočiti potez pritiskom na <guibutton>End Turn</guibutton> bez "
"lansiranja brodova."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Strategije i Savjeti"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The game is all about ship production. Try to get as many planets as "
"possible as fast as you can in order to build more ships than any of your "
"opponents."
msgstr ""
"Igra je sve o proizvodnji brodova. Pokušajte da osvojite što više planeta "
"što brže kako bi mogli da pravite više brodova od vaših protivnika."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Do not attack a planet with less than 10 ships, unless you can conquer it."
msgstr ""
"Ne napadajte planetu sa manje od 10 brodova, osim ako je možete osvojiti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Attack neutral planets before other players' planets."
msgstr "Napadnite neutralne planete prije planeta drugih igrača."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid "Split your ship storages across several planets."
msgstr "Podijelite zalihe vaših brodova na nekoliko planeta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plan your attacks in advance."
msgstr "Planirajte vaše napade unaprijed."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use the ruler to find out the distance between planets."
msgstr "Koristite linijar da odredite udaljenost između planeta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the information window to get information on planets before an attack."
msgstr ""
"Koristite prozor za informacije kako bi dobili informacije o planetama prije "
"nego ih napadnete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this information is available to you, it is preferable to attack a planet "
"with a low kill ratio from a planet with a high one."
msgstr ""
"Ako je ova informacija dostupna vama, poželjno je da napadnete planet sa "
"malim procentom ubijanja nego planet sa velikim procentom ubijanja."

