#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "Često postavljana pitanja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I redirect ships once they have left a planet?"
msgstr "Mogu li promijeniti putanju brodova ako su već napustili planet?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "No, once ships leave a planet, they cannot be stopped or redirected."
msgstr ""
"Ne, jednom kad brod napusti planet, ne mogu biti zaustavljeni ili "
"promijeniti putanju."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do the different colors and shapes of planets mean anything?"
msgstr "Da li drugačije boje i oblici planeta predstavljau išta?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid "No, they are random."
msgstr "Ne, oni su nasumični."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I know where my ships are?"
msgstr "Kako mogu zanti gdje se nalaze moji brodovi?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click <guibutton>Show Standings</guibutton>. It will give you information "
"about fleets currently in flight."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite na <guibutton>Show Standings</guibutton>. To će vam dati "
"informaciju o flotama trenutno u brobi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid "I have lost all my planets, but I am still in the game, why?"
msgstr "Izgubio sam sve planete, ali sam i dalje u igri, zašto?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "You have not lost the game until you have lost all your ships."
msgstr "Niste izgubili igru  dok ne izgubite sve brodove."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I store ships on a planet for later use?"
msgstr "Mogu li pohraniti brodove na planetu za kasniju upotrebu?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes, you should however store them on multiple planets to be able to send "
"them to nearby planets."
msgstr ""
"Da, međutim treba li biste ih pohraniti na više planeta da biste ih mogli "
"poslati na obližnje planete."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "Is it possible to change the theme?"
msgstr "Da li je moguće promijeniti temu?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid "No, that is not possible at the moment."
msgstr "Ne, to trenutno nije moguće."

